flowchart TD
    F((F)) --> Load[Load map + query incidents]
    Load --> Mode{View mode?}

    Mode -- Heatmap --> Heat[Density gradient from incident locations<br/>green to red = fewer to more crimes]
    Mode -- Pins --> Pins[Numbered circles per sitio]

    Heat --> Filter
    Pins --> Filter
    Filter{Apply filter?}
    Filter -- Date range / crime type --> Re[Re-render layer for filtered set]
    Filter -- No --> Show

    Re --> Show[Show density + sitio ranking + recent incidents]
    Show --> Click{Click an incident dot?}
    Click -- Yes --> Pop[Show incident details popup]
    Click -- No --> R((R))
    Pop --> R
